<item>
            <title>[LU-15410] Add MDS Space check for dom-performance/IOR TEST</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15410</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&#160;IOR Test within dom-performance requires at least 20GB MDS. Otherwise the IOR test fails with &quot;Out of Space&quot; error.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;--------------------------------------------------------------------------&lt;br/&gt;
WARNING: Task 0, partial write(), 4096 of 8192 bytes at offset 98304&lt;br/&gt;
ior ERROR: write() failed, errno 28, No space left on device (aiori-POSIX.c:451)&lt;br/&gt;
--------------------------------------------------------------------------&lt;br/&gt;
MPI_ABORT was invoked on rank 2 in communicator MPI_COMM_WORLD&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
with errorcode -1.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
